These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, fonseca, aristoff, siglo
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, egyptian, thai, turkish
1. the egyptian is on the left of the chinese##1
2. the baccarat-smoker is the turkish##1
3. the thai is on the right of the chinese##1
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the turkish##1
5. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Cigar          | siglo | aristoff | fonseca | baccarat   |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | chinese     | thai   | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, lime, peas, pear
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person eating lime##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person eating peas##1
5. the person eating lime is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| Food   | peas    | lime      | strawberry | pear |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, r&b, classical, soul
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, mystery, time-travel
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the fan of blues is the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the fan of soul##1
5. the fan of classical is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Music-Genre         | blues | soul | classical   | r&b |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | mystery | time-travel | drama         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, drama, western
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, october, august, september
1. the person who's birthday is in october is the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | western | disaster | action  | drama      |
| Birthday         | october | september   | august | november |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, cucumber, kiwi, pineapple
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, chef, security-guard, bartender
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the security-guard is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the bartender##1
4. the chef is on the right of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | pineapple | kiwi | cucumber | cauliflower |
| Job    | fisherman       | bartender | security-guard | chef     |

