3. the lawyer is on the left of the librarian##1
4. the engineer is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the lawyer is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | nigerian | dutch | mexican |
| Job           | engineer      | police-officer | lawyer | librarian    |

