2. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
3. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | indie | electronic | classical | salsa  |
| Movie-Genre           | martial-arts | western | thriller       | horror |

