2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
