.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, snake, turtle, chinchilla
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | cola | milk  | hot-chocolate | sprite |
| Pet   | chinchilla | turtle | snake          | goldfish    |

