.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, sprite, water
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, aconite, marigold, balloon-flower
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking milk is the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | sprite | milk  | hot-chocolate | water |
| Flower   | bellflower  | marigold | balloon-flower           | aconite   |

