.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, lacrosse, parkour, biathlon
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, frog, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Sport   | lacrosse | rugby | biathlon | parkour  |
| Pet           | hedgehog | fish      | frog | ferret |

