.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
House: gothic-revival, victorian, wooden, ranch-style
4 different pets are kept: hamster, lizard, rabbit, rat
1. the owner of the rat is the gothic-revival house##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
3. the wooden house is the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the wooden house is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the ranch-style house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| House   | wooden | victorian  | gothic-revival | ranch-style   |
| Pet        | rabbit | lizard | rat    | hamster |

