.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, puzzles, rock-climbing, video-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, water-polo, biathlon
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | puzzles | rock-climbing | video-games | cooking |
| Sport   | biathlon     | water-polo    | climbing      | cycling   |

