.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, mexican, nigerian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, superhero, horror, fantasy
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the american is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the nigerian is the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | american | mexican | argentine | nigerian   |
| Movie-Genre     | horror  | comedy    | superhero       | fantasy |

 